    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to vehicle.msrp_pricing. Business justification: The quote process must reference the authoritative MSRP pricing record for price audit trails, regulatory price disclosure compliance, and dealer margin calculation. Linking quote to msrp_pricing ensu' ;
