    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to manufacturing.plant. Business justification: BOM headers in automotive are plant-specific — a product BOM is released to a specific manufacturing plant for production execution. Plant-specific BOM management is standard SAP PP practice; plant_co' ;
