    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to compliance.fmvss_certification. Business justification: FMVSS certifications (US market) require crash and safety test evidence. NCAP test results are the specific test records that substantiate FMVSS certification filings. Compliance engineers reference e' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:Automotive ;
